name: Xeno Tezors #05 - Yyirrr
description: As far as known Yyirrr is the last remaining survivor of a hyper intelligent lizard race. Also she is one of the best headhunters known in the universe travelling restless to find the most dangerous and honorable headhunter assignments. Her intelligence and precision are only matched by her cruelty against her targets. Only weak point: Once she smells the sweet taste of blood and flesh she completely loses control over herself.
